---

<section class="hero" aria-labelledby="hero-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div>
        <h1 id="hero-heading">I build teams<br />that <em>build<br />products.</em></h1>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-right">
        <p>Engineering leader with 18+ years of experience shipping software — from hands-on architecture to building teams and delivery processes that scale. I've taken products from first commit to market across fintech, travel, e-commerce, and Web3.</p>
        <dl class="hero-meta">
          <div>
            <dt>Experience</dt>
            <dd>18+ years</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt>Teams led</dt>
            <dd>Up to 15+</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt>Products</dt>
            <dd>6+ shipped</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt>Based in</dt>
            <dd>Granada, Spain</dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding-top: 60px;
  }

  .hero-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: center;
    width: 100%;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 5vw, 4.2rem);
    line-height: 1.08;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference) {
    h1 {
      animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease both;
    }
    .hero-right p {
      animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease 0.15s both;
    }
    .hero-meta {
      animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease 0.3s both;
    }
  }

  h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .hero-right p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    max-width: 420px;
  }

  .hero-meta {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .hero-meta dt {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .hero-meta dd {
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(24px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }
    .hero-meta {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }
</style>
